1
00:00:31,000 --> 00:00:33,320
[You Have My Heart]

2
00:00:33,340 --> 00:00:36,360
[Episode 19 The Gilded Cage]

3
00:01:11,720 --> 00:01:12,280
Yu.

4
00:01:12,600 --> 00:01:14,000
Are you feeling alright?

5
00:01:26,600 --> 00:01:28,070
The mortal body

6
00:01:29,700 --> 00:01:30,950
is truly

7
00:01:32,750 --> 00:01:34,479
so fragile.

8
00:01:38,670 --> 00:01:39,420
Who are you?

9
00:01:40,759 --> 00:01:41,560
Who are you?

10
00:01:42,789 --> 00:01:44,200
You're not my son!

11
00:01:44,550 --> 00:01:45,750
What did you do to him?

12
00:01:46,060 --> 00:01:48,090
The original owner
of this body was destroyed,

13
00:01:48,090 --> 00:01:51,150
and his soul scattered to nothingness
the moment you drew that final stroke.

14
00:01:51,150 --> 00:01:53,280
the moment you drew that final stroke.

15
00:01:54,350 --> 00:01:56,560
Now, it belongs to me.

16
00:01:57,590 --> 00:01:58,759
Give me back my son!

17
00:01:59,930 --> 00:02:01,330
I'll fight you to the death!

18
00:02:01,330 --> 00:02:02,590
I'll fight you to the death!

19
00:02:02,590 --> 00:02:03,790
I'll strangle you...

20
00:02:03,860 --> 00:02:05,390
I'll fight you to the death!

21
00:02:12,290 --> 00:02:14,890
Qian Wanqian

22
00:02:15,410 --> 00:02:16,760
Calm down.

23
00:02:17,190 --> 00:02:19,520
What your son traded his life for

24
00:02:19,540 --> 00:02:21,340
is far beyond your imagination.

25
00:02:26,150 --> 00:02:27,430
This gold mine alone

26
00:02:27,520 --> 00:02:30,170
is enough to make you
richer than a nation.

27
00:02:30,710 --> 00:02:33,490
And this is only the beginning.

28
00:02:33,980 --> 00:02:37,140
Are you willing to spend your life

29
00:02:37,780 --> 00:02:39,380
under Liu Fufeng's control,

30
00:02:39,800 --> 00:02:41,430
living as a wealthy man

31
00:02:41,430 --> 00:02:43,400
who must read her every expression

32
00:02:44,260 --> 00:02:45,700
and act on her every whim?

33
00:02:47,850 --> 00:02:50,360
If I become the true master

34
00:02:50,540 --> 00:02:51,980
of Yin-Yang Crossing,

35
00:02:53,050 --> 00:02:54,400
you will be

36
00:02:55,070 --> 00:02:56,600
my greatest merit subject,

37
00:02:57,560 --> 00:03:01,280
as if walking with a god.

38
00:03:04,900 --> 00:03:07,830
Is that not enough to ease even a trace

39
00:03:08,290 --> 00:03:11,690
of your insignificant
grief over losing your son?

40
00:03:18,579 --> 00:03:19,370
Master.

41
00:03:20,590 --> 00:03:22,190
The ore vein has been opened.

42
00:03:23,060 --> 00:03:24,620
It can be mined at any time.

43
00:03:35,290 --> 00:03:36,820
Each time Master meets him,

44
00:03:37,070 --> 00:03:39,400
Young Master Yulang's body ages further.

45
00:04:44,750 --> 00:04:45,840
Found it.

46
00:04:46,370 --> 00:04:47,930
Finally found it.

47
00:04:48,270 --> 00:04:51,600
This is the perfect vessel!

48
00:04:52,740 --> 00:04:53,470
Go—

49
00:04:54,350 --> 00:04:57,550
inscribe the corruption-inducing talisman
on his body.

50
00:04:59,480 --> 00:05:00,950
Come back here tomorrow

51
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:03,080
at this hour

52
00:05:04,010 --> 00:05:06,490
to collect your son's corpse—Qian Yulang.

53
00:05:09,340 --> 00:05:10,770
No one could have predicted it—

54
00:05:10,770 --> 00:05:12,700
an accident happened the next day.

55
00:05:21,240 --> 00:05:21,830
Master,

56
00:05:22,730 --> 00:05:23,660
what is going on?

57
00:05:25,060 --> 00:05:26,380
Something went wrong

58
00:05:27,930 --> 00:05:29,120
during possession.

59
00:05:29,870 --> 00:05:32,790
His nature is too pure and stubborn.

60
00:05:33,190 --> 00:05:36,390
He actually purified
the corruption-inducing talisman

61
00:05:36,900 --> 00:05:37,900
on his back.

62
00:05:38,690 --> 00:05:39,940
He broke free from me

63
00:05:40,350 --> 00:05:42,150
and escaped with the tree heart.

64
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:45,830
Don't worry, I'll go right away.

65
00:05:45,870 --> 00:05:46,720
No need.

66
00:05:50,730 --> 00:05:51,940
At this moment,

67
00:05:53,070 --> 00:05:55,320
he has already met Liu Fufeng.

68
00:05:58,100 --> 00:06:00,660
We'll need
to take a long-term view of this.

69
00:06:05,190 --> 00:06:06,190
Take a close look—

70
00:06:06,770 --> 00:06:09,900
was the abandoned,

71
00:06:09,990 --> 00:06:11,590
withered body in that cave

72
00:06:12,050 --> 00:06:13,280
like this?

73
00:06:13,480 --> 00:06:14,280
Yes, it's him.

74
00:06:14,430 --> 00:06:16,880
That is exactly what Young Master Yulang
looked like in the end.

75
00:06:16,880 --> 00:06:19,380
No wonder we deployed
all of Xiqianhua's resources

76
00:06:19,380 --> 00:06:20,410
and still couldn't find

77
00:06:20,410 --> 00:06:22,930
any trace of that
one-eyed old man's records.

78
00:06:22,930 --> 00:06:23,740
So you found

79
00:06:24,900 --> 00:06:26,730
the Sun's Bakery

80
00:06:27,490 --> 00:06:30,570
because it was bait he deliberately set.

81
00:06:31,160 --> 00:06:32,850
He knew you would
investigate the talisman,

82
00:06:32,850 --> 00:06:34,530
so he appeared there on purpose—

83
00:06:34,530 --> 00:06:35,610
just to lure you

84
00:06:35,760 --> 00:06:38,320
back into his territory again

85
00:06:38,610 --> 00:06:41,010
and seize the body

86
00:06:41,270 --> 00:06:43,159
he had long been coveting.

87
00:06:44,720 --> 00:06:46,720
Now that his scheme has failed,

88
00:06:47,100 --> 00:06:48,610
he's switched to another vessel

89
00:06:48,610 --> 00:06:52,340
and created something like the so-called
Fortune-Turning Stone.

90
00:06:53,270 --> 00:06:56,270
Let's talk about
the Fortune-Turning Master now.

91
00:06:57,180 --> 00:06:59,310
That was another tragedy altogether.

92
00:06:59,560 --> 00:07:01,960
After the evil entity
was severely wounded

93
00:07:02,110 --> 00:07:04,040
and left without a body to inhabit,

94
00:07:05,020 --> 00:07:07,280
it set its sights on Master's second son—

95
00:07:08,440 --> 00:07:09,560
Jinlang.

96
00:07:12,980 --> 00:07:13,590
Jinlang,

97
00:07:15,510 --> 00:07:16,370
don't blame me.

98
00:07:16,760 --> 00:07:18,080
I have no choice.

99
00:07:20,180 --> 00:07:23,630
I am doing this
for the future of our Qian family.

100
00:07:25,270 --> 00:07:26,800
The Master said it himself—

101
00:07:28,440 --> 00:07:31,000
it's only a temporary use of your body.

102
00:07:31,720 --> 00:07:34,640
In the future, he will grant

103
00:07:35,680 --> 00:07:37,880
our Qian family wealth and prosperity.

104
00:07:56,520 --> 00:07:57,350
Master,

105
00:07:57,930 --> 00:07:59,930
for today's batch of goods,

106
00:08:00,340 --> 00:08:03,580
may I ask if you see any suitable vessel?

107
00:08:04,190 --> 00:08:05,390
If so,

108
00:08:06,070 --> 00:08:09,730
I will immediately inscribe
the corruption-inducing talisman.

109
00:08:16,160 --> 00:08:16,950
What,

110
00:08:17,780 --> 00:08:20,710
already feeling sorry
for your youngest son's body?

111
00:08:22,530 --> 00:08:23,410
Don't worry.

112
00:08:24,040 --> 00:08:25,190
What I promised you,

113
00:08:25,490 --> 00:08:26,960
I will keep.

114
00:08:26,980 --> 00:08:27,560
Understood.

115
00:08:27,560 --> 00:08:30,020
It's only a temporary borrowing
of his body.

116
00:08:30,950 --> 00:08:32,000
Understood, understood.

117
00:08:32,000 --> 00:08:33,289
That was my overstep.

118
00:08:33,640 --> 00:08:34,640
I will

119
00:08:34,750 --> 00:08:37,710
continue searching
for suitable vessels for you.

120
00:08:40,640 --> 00:08:42,039
Where is your thumb ring?

121
00:08:46,480 --> 00:08:47,390
Master,

122
00:08:47,440 --> 00:08:49,790
the ring's spiritual power
seems to have been clouded.

123
00:08:49,790 --> 00:08:53,150
I have already sent it to Elder Cha

124
00:08:53,510 --> 00:08:56,060
to be nourished for a few days,

125
00:08:56,460 --> 00:08:59,460
in hopes that it can regain
its spiritual connection

126
00:08:59,490 --> 00:09:01,610
and better assist your grand plan.

127
00:09:04,450 --> 00:09:05,620
It had better be so.

128
00:09:08,310 --> 00:09:09,310
However, Master,

129
00:09:10,280 --> 00:09:12,840
the outside situation
has become increasingly tense.

130
00:09:12,840 --> 00:09:15,240
Because of the previous incident,

131
00:09:15,810 --> 00:09:18,770
the public now is uncertain
about the Fortune-Turning Master.

132
00:09:18,770 --> 00:09:19,890
More importantly,

133
00:09:20,160 --> 00:09:22,070
Xiqianhua and the authorities

134
00:09:22,650 --> 00:09:25,250
are watching us more closely than ever.

135
00:09:25,600 --> 00:09:26,290
The mine

136
00:09:26,500 --> 00:09:28,240
cannot be exhausted in a single day,

137
00:09:28,240 --> 00:09:29,080
nor will the mountain

138
00:09:29,080 --> 00:09:30,960
collapse overnight.

139
00:09:32,430 --> 00:09:33,280
We are

140
00:09:33,400 --> 00:09:34,950
only just beginning.

141
00:09:35,850 --> 00:09:38,280
Have you released the people?

142
00:09:39,460 --> 00:09:41,330
[County Yamen]

143
00:09:41,810 --> 00:09:44,390
If only I hadn't persuaded my husband

144
00:09:44,410 --> 00:09:45,740
to hand over that stone.

145
00:09:46,720 --> 00:09:49,790
Otherwise,
he wouldn't have been taken away.

146
00:09:49,790 --> 00:09:50,550
We trusted

147
00:09:50,550 --> 00:09:53,480
Liu Fufeng too much in everything.

148
00:09:55,000 --> 00:09:56,310
We're just mortals—

149
00:09:56,690 --> 00:09:59,620
how could we ever outwit
a thousand-year-old demon?

150
00:09:59,950 --> 00:10:01,010
Now, I just want him

151
00:10:01,310 --> 00:10:03,190
to return my father to me.

152
00:10:04,490 --> 00:10:09,280
Whispers echo in the forest,
each cry like weeping.

153
00:10:09,730 --> 00:10:13,820
Mimicking human speech,
it drains away vitality.

154
00:10:15,840 --> 00:10:19,720
Old things return,
shifting within the heart.

155
00:10:21,370 --> 00:10:26,040
Not their rightful owner—
calamity will not cease.

156
00:10:27,030 --> 00:10:28,790
The tree demon Liu Fufeng,

157
00:10:29,520 --> 00:10:31,980
jealous of Bai Han—
the descendant of Pangu—

158
00:10:32,440 --> 00:10:34,230
covets his power

159
00:10:34,630 --> 00:10:36,890
and stole his source of spiritual power:

160
00:10:36,960 --> 00:10:39,440
that heart imbued with it.

161
00:10:40,550 --> 00:10:42,280
Bai Shanjun and Liu Fufeng

162
00:10:42,300 --> 00:10:43,740
present themselves as righteous,

163
00:10:43,740 --> 00:10:46,140
but in truth
they are engaged in depravity.

164
00:10:46,760 --> 00:10:49,490
The one who suppresses
calamity has lost virtue;

165
00:10:49,550 --> 00:10:51,480
yin and yang are thrown into chaos.

166
00:10:52,070 --> 00:10:54,800
If Yin-Yang Crossing
does not change its master,

167
00:10:54,880 --> 00:10:57,000
it will be devoured by evil power

168
00:10:57,510 --> 00:10:59,240
and suffer eternal damnation.

169
00:11:00,510 --> 00:11:02,750
And you all still believe Liu Fufeng?

170
00:11:03,860 --> 00:11:04,930
Just wait—

171
00:11:07,240 --> 00:11:08,790
Yin-Yang Crossing

172
00:11:11,120 --> 00:11:12,450
is done for.

173
00:11:15,640 --> 00:11:16,950
A descendant of Pangu

174
00:11:17,070 --> 00:11:19,670
sounds more reliable
than a tree demon.

175
00:11:19,900 --> 00:11:22,230
All these years—we've all been deceived.

176
00:11:23,310 --> 00:11:24,280
It was them.

177
00:11:24,540 --> 00:11:26,250
It was them who wanted
to take away all the stones

178
00:11:26,250 --> 00:11:27,850
from the Fortune-Turning Master—

179
00:11:27,850 --> 00:11:30,210
and in the end, people got arrested.

180
00:11:30,230 --> 00:11:32,060
Give me back my husband!

181
00:11:32,450 --> 00:11:33,930
Give him back!

182
00:11:33,960 --> 00:11:36,100
Ever since that so-called Magistrate Bai
came to Yin-Yang Crossing,

183
00:11:36,100 --> 00:11:37,250
people have been dying nonstop.

184
00:11:37,250 --> 00:11:39,420
And Liu Fufeng has
only gotten closer and closer to him.

185
00:11:39,420 --> 00:11:41,690
There might be something going on.

186
00:11:42,280 --> 00:11:43,130
Demons—

187
00:11:43,250 --> 00:11:44,850
give me back my family!
Give me back my family!

188
00:11:44,850 --> 00:11:46,060
Give me back my husband!

189
00:11:46,060 --> 00:11:47,660
Give me back my family!

190
00:11:47,690 --> 00:11:49,060
Give me back my husband!

191
00:11:49,080 --> 00:11:50,070
Give us our family back!

192
00:11:50,070 --> 00:11:51,710
Give back my husband!

193
00:11:52,330 --> 00:11:53,560
Deluding the masses!

194
00:11:53,880 --> 00:11:55,490
Give me back my husband!

195
00:12:07,440 --> 00:12:08,040
Shuan.

196
00:12:08,430 --> 00:12:10,630
They're even killing their own people!

197
00:12:10,710 --> 00:12:13,240
Fengling, I'll take him
for treatment first.

198
00:12:13,900 --> 00:12:15,870
There's evil power
gathering inside Shuan's body.

199
00:12:15,870 --> 00:12:17,410
This is corruption purge
using spiritual power—

200
00:12:17,410 --> 00:12:18,530
he's not dead.

201
00:12:18,900 --> 00:12:21,100
Anyone who dares spout nonsense again,

202
00:12:21,200 --> 00:12:23,630
I'll cut out their tongue!

203
00:12:29,980 --> 00:12:31,800
What about the people who were taken?

204
00:12:31,800 --> 00:12:32,700
And what she just used—

205
00:12:32,700 --> 00:12:35,070
wasn't that also some kind of power
we've never seen before?

206
00:12:35,070 --> 00:12:36,460
She says it's spiritual power,

207
00:12:36,460 --> 00:12:38,270
but—but the way she kills...

208
00:12:38,290 --> 00:12:40,820
how is that any different
from the evil power?

209
00:12:40,970 --> 00:12:43,900
Silencing witnesses—
this is silencing witnesses!

210
00:12:43,900 --> 00:12:45,380
As soon as Shuan spoke the truth,

211
00:12:45,380 --> 00:12:46,620
they killed him.

212
00:12:47,780 --> 00:12:49,660
No matter who's right or wrong,

213
00:12:50,810 --> 00:12:52,480
when gods fight,

214
00:12:52,970 --> 00:12:55,300
aren't the ones who die
and turn to ashes

215
00:12:55,720 --> 00:12:57,840
us ordinary people?

216
00:12:58,030 --> 00:12:59,630
Yeah, exactly.

217
00:12:59,650 --> 00:13:00,620
Could it be...

218
00:13:01,160 --> 00:13:03,380
Yin-Yang Crossing is really finished?

219
00:13:03,400 --> 00:13:04,720
Is there anyone
who cares whether we live or die?

220
00:13:04,720 --> 00:13:06,870
What about our family?

221
00:13:07,000 --> 00:13:08,240
What are we supposed to do?

222
00:13:08,240 --> 00:13:10,500
what am I supposed to do about my husband?

223
00:13:11,220 --> 00:13:13,090
[Xiqianhua Mansion]

224
00:13:32,650 --> 00:13:35,290
Can Shuan still return to normal?

225
00:13:38,030 --> 00:13:40,090
The evil power has corroded his soul.

226
00:13:40,430 --> 00:13:42,400
We can barely keep him alive—

227
00:13:43,370 --> 00:13:45,280
like that child in red robes,

228
00:13:46,160 --> 00:13:48,290
he can never return to what he once was.

229
00:13:51,070 --> 00:13:52,880
Is Shuan really beyond saving?

230
00:13:54,170 --> 00:13:55,380
He's just a child.

231
00:13:57,030 --> 00:13:58,030
How is he supposed

232
00:13:58,690 --> 00:14:00,400
to live like this from now on?

233
00:14:02,500 --> 00:14:03,310
Bai Han,

234
00:14:03,870 --> 00:14:04,940
that bastard!

235
00:14:05,320 --> 00:14:07,920
He's trying to destroy
our Yin-Yang Crossing!

236
00:14:07,920 --> 00:14:09,160
I want him dead!

237
00:14:23,270 --> 00:14:24,360
Let them go.

238
00:14:28,960 --> 00:14:29,650
My Lady.

239
00:14:30,070 --> 00:14:32,000
In recent days,
one tragedy after another has occurred.

240
00:14:32,000 --> 00:14:33,630
And regarding the Fortune-Turning Master,

241
00:14:33,630 --> 00:14:35,360
more people have gone missing,

242
00:14:35,360 --> 00:14:37,760
and rumors are spreading among the people.

243
00:14:37,960 --> 00:14:41,160
As for what happened today,
do not let it chill your heart.

244
00:14:46,150 --> 00:14:48,880
My Lady, you don't have to pretend
you don't care—

245
00:14:49,730 --> 00:14:51,080
I can feel it too.

246
00:14:54,330 --> 00:14:56,880
Today, I also feel uneasy.

247
00:14:58,430 --> 00:15:00,090
The people are simple-minded

248
00:15:00,090 --> 00:15:01,300
and easily tempted.

249
00:15:01,970 --> 00:15:02,970
But this Bai Han—

250
00:15:03,240 --> 00:15:05,080
after abducting so many people,
that is still not enough;

251
00:15:05,080 --> 00:15:08,150
he now wants to further plunge
Yin-Yang Crossing into chaos.

252
00:15:08,150 --> 00:15:09,950
I'm afraid it's not that simple.

253
00:15:10,430 --> 00:15:11,630
Do you still remember

254
00:15:12,630 --> 00:15:14,120
what Bai Han said before?

255
00:15:15,930 --> 00:15:19,130
As long as evil power does not perish,
neither will I.

256
00:15:19,900 --> 00:15:24,100
Liu Fufeng, we have a long future ahead.

257
00:15:25,040 --> 00:15:26,520
My Lady, do you mean

258
00:15:27,120 --> 00:15:28,920
he was not merely exaggerating?

259
00:15:29,000 --> 00:15:32,400
And that his spiritual consciousness and
evil power have already fused into one?

260
00:15:32,400 --> 00:15:33,400
Very likely.

261
00:15:34,390 --> 00:15:36,540
Just like the evil power
within Shuan's body—

262
00:15:36,540 --> 00:15:39,070
that is only a manifested
fragment of Bai Han.

263
00:15:39,390 --> 00:15:42,060
He can discard it at will
once it has served its purpose.

264
00:15:42,060 --> 00:15:43,670
If he has fused
his spiritual consciousness

265
00:15:43,670 --> 00:15:46,630
into the evil power network within
the earth veins of Yin-Yang Crossing,

266
00:15:46,630 --> 00:15:47,630
then he

267
00:15:48,510 --> 00:15:49,840
will be everywhere.

268
00:15:50,910 --> 00:15:52,240
What we are facing

269
00:15:52,600 --> 00:15:55,000
is no longer an enemy hiding
in the shadows,

270
00:15:55,030 --> 00:15:56,840
but the evil power itself

271
00:15:57,960 --> 00:15:59,560
beneath Yin-Yang Crossing.

272
00:16:00,620 --> 00:16:01,950
The urgent priority now

273
00:16:02,390 --> 00:16:04,250
is to find the missing civilians.

274
00:16:04,910 --> 00:16:07,910
Where could they be hidden?

275
00:16:19,910 --> 00:16:21,580
Since when did you start getting

276
00:16:21,580 --> 00:16:23,890
all sentimental like Lord Bai?

277
00:16:24,790 --> 00:16:25,600
What?

278
00:16:26,020 --> 00:16:27,830
You think I'm just some goofy simpleton?

279
00:16:27,830 --> 00:16:29,560
I've got worries too, you know.

280
00:16:30,000 --> 00:16:31,120
Worries?

281
00:16:32,040 --> 00:16:33,160
Don't be gross.

282
00:16:39,730 --> 00:16:42,060
You're thinking about Shuan,
aren't you?

283
00:16:47,840 --> 00:16:49,300
Do you think that kid Shuan

284
00:16:49,720 --> 00:16:50,910
will be okay?

285
00:16:52,720 --> 00:16:53,510
Anyway,

286
00:16:54,630 --> 00:16:56,690
my master will do everything she can.

287
00:16:56,840 --> 00:16:57,970
Don't overthink it.

288
00:16:59,230 --> 00:17:00,840
Honestly, this is also partly my fault.

289
00:17:00,840 --> 00:17:02,370
If I had noticed earlier...

290
00:17:06,480 --> 00:17:07,829
Come on, you're a girl—

291
00:17:07,829 --> 00:17:09,720
stop always getting physical, alright?

292
00:17:09,720 --> 00:17:11,400
I'm not a girl to begin with.

293
00:17:11,910 --> 00:17:14,260
I'm a bell.

294
00:17:16,440 --> 00:17:19,119
Enough being dramatic.

295
00:17:19,589 --> 00:17:21,030
Her ladyship and His Lordship
have new leads—

296
00:17:21,030 --> 00:17:21,960
back to work.

297
00:17:23,260 --> 00:17:24,260
Hey, Bell Spirit—

298
00:17:24,530 --> 00:17:25,329
wait for me.

299
00:17:27,270 --> 00:17:29,940
Master brought me into the mountains
through a secret passage of the bank.

300
00:17:29,940 --> 00:17:31,700
First, we passed through
a long mining tunnel,

301
00:17:31,700 --> 00:17:34,200
with traces of man-made excavation
on both sides,

302
00:17:34,200 --> 00:17:36,600
leading toward the main pit
where gold was extracted.

303
00:17:36,600 --> 00:17:38,280
The main pit was immense,

304
00:17:38,300 --> 00:17:39,500
but it wasn't the end.

305
00:17:39,650 --> 00:17:41,730
On one flank,

306
00:17:41,830 --> 00:17:43,690
rough-hewn steps coiled upward—

307
00:17:44,000 --> 00:17:46,750
and at their summit
stood the Gilded Grotto.

308
00:17:48,480 --> 00:17:50,280
It was not an ordinary dwelling,

309
00:17:50,480 --> 00:17:52,400
but a hidden residence
carved out within the mountain itself—

310
00:17:52,400 --> 00:17:54,440
its pillars made of ore,

311
00:17:54,440 --> 00:17:56,170
and its lamps of colored glass.

312
00:17:56,890 --> 00:18:00,240
The walls were covered
with strange patterns,

313
00:18:00,910 --> 00:18:04,110
the same as those tattooed
on Young Master Yulang's back.

314
00:18:09,960 --> 00:18:10,730
My Lady,

315
00:18:11,480 --> 00:18:13,640
is this a corruption-inducing talisman?

316
00:18:13,640 --> 00:18:16,590
It should be an artificially constructed
"eye of evil power" created by Bai Han.

317
00:18:16,590 --> 00:18:17,840
With this formation,

318
00:18:18,110 --> 00:18:19,510
he can draw in evil power.

319
00:18:19,760 --> 00:18:21,630
In other words,

320
00:18:21,870 --> 00:18:23,880
he can freely control evil power here.

321
00:18:23,880 --> 00:18:25,480
As long as evil power exists,

322
00:18:25,640 --> 00:18:28,110
his power seems limitless.

323
00:18:28,420 --> 00:18:31,390
This cave is extremely well hidden—
hard to detect.

324
00:18:34,010 --> 00:18:35,060
And this mountain

325
00:18:35,440 --> 00:18:37,680
seems to be already at the boundary
of Yin-Yang Crossing.

326
00:18:37,680 --> 00:18:38,480
That's right.

327
00:18:39,110 --> 00:18:41,840
This gold mine is built
on the Yin-Yang boundary,

328
00:18:41,900 --> 00:18:44,380
and his lair lies outside the boundary,

329
00:18:46,020 --> 00:18:47,260
beyond my reach.

330
00:18:48,330 --> 00:18:49,130
Why?

331
00:18:49,590 --> 00:18:50,720
My Lady, haven't you

332
00:18:50,730 --> 00:18:52,590
already obtained the complete tree heart?

333
00:18:52,590 --> 00:18:54,730
Your spiritual power now far surpasses
what it once was.

334
00:18:54,730 --> 00:18:57,200
Could you still not suppress Bai Han?

335
00:19:00,510 --> 00:19:02,110
Over the past hundred years,

336
00:19:02,350 --> 00:19:05,150
I have placed seals
throughout Yin-Yang Crossing

337
00:19:05,510 --> 00:19:08,000
to lock down the surging evil power
beneath the ground.

338
00:19:08,000 --> 00:19:09,850
But the moment I step
beyond the boundary

339
00:19:09,850 --> 00:19:11,310
and away from my true body,

340
00:19:11,550 --> 00:19:14,020
that evil power will erupt—

341
00:19:15,510 --> 00:19:16,710
and the harm it causes

342
00:19:16,930 --> 00:19:19,110
will be far beyond
what either of us can imagine.

343
00:19:19,110 --> 00:19:19,950
So

344
00:19:20,390 --> 00:19:22,320
he deliberately chose this place—

345
00:19:22,540 --> 00:19:23,930
a location you can see,

346
00:19:23,960 --> 00:19:25,380
yet cannot reach or assault.

347
00:19:25,380 --> 00:19:27,900
An absolute safe zone for him.

348
00:19:39,240 --> 00:19:40,240
In that case,

349
00:19:40,870 --> 00:19:41,830
I'll go.

350
00:19:47,000 --> 00:19:47,810
No.

351
00:19:50,500 --> 00:19:51,610
A dying man

352
00:19:52,240 --> 00:19:53,840
should die where he belongs.

353
00:19:54,830 --> 00:19:57,490
Don't talk about death like that—
it's bad luck.

354
00:19:59,570 --> 00:20:00,360
My Lady,

355
00:20:00,510 --> 00:20:03,110
this is a certain-death
situation for you,

356
00:20:03,220 --> 00:20:05,640
because you cannot afford
to lose Yin-Yang Crossing.

357
00:20:05,640 --> 00:20:06,640
For me as well,

358
00:20:06,850 --> 00:20:08,640
it is a certain-death situation.

359
00:20:08,640 --> 00:20:09,640
But I don't have

360
00:20:09,660 --> 00:20:10,920
much time left anyway.

361
00:20:11,320 --> 00:20:12,980
If I use this dying body of mine

362
00:20:13,010 --> 00:20:15,590
to trade for a chance
to break this deadlock...

363
00:20:15,590 --> 00:20:16,670
then even if I die,

364
00:20:16,960 --> 00:20:19,640
I can still save the people
of Yin-Yang Crossing.

365
00:20:19,640 --> 00:20:21,700
And if it fails, we will lose nothing.

366
00:20:27,430 --> 00:20:28,240
Do you think

367
00:20:28,960 --> 00:20:30,070
you're a hero?

368
00:20:33,310 --> 00:20:34,110
My Lady,

369
00:20:34,770 --> 00:20:36,240
I, Bai Shanjun,

370
00:20:36,430 --> 00:20:38,560
have never thought of myself as a hero.

371
00:20:38,880 --> 00:20:40,130
I'm just a small magistrate

372
00:20:40,130 --> 00:20:42,130
who wants to finish what he should do

373
00:20:42,160 --> 00:20:43,080
in the end.
